The audience of fashion dolls is filled with names like Sibilla of Luxembourg, Gloria of Thurn and Taxis, Mette-Marit of Norway, Rosario of Bulgaria, and Sofía of Habsburg.
Naty Abascal and the Fashion Designer, 2006
