"I prefer him to everyone else because of his great love for women and because he highlights our beauty", adds the former Duchess of Feria.
I really like the colors he uses; they have a lot of light and emphasize the face.
The proportions are perfect.
Even the princess and fashion icon Patricia della Giovampaola d'Arenberg can't forget the first time she wore a Valentino.
When I was a teenager living in Italy, I dreamed of finally being old enough to wear one of his evening dresses...
And then, in the late '90s, it finally came to this.
